data.description: Welcome to this charming Cozy Bungalow, a hidden gem offering comfort and potential in every corner. With 2 full bathrooms and the convenience of main level laundry, this home effortlessly combines functionality with ease of living. The large garage-like space is a treasure trove providing ample room for all your belongings. The spacious driveway can accommodate multiple vehicles. The property boasts a newer metal roof and presents an incredible opportunity for you to make it your own. With its great rental potential, this Cozy Bungalow presents an enticing investment prospect. Come and see the potential that awaits in this hidden gem!
